name: Register RCVTRK registeration for WMD1 warehouse
command:
register ossi object instances created
where wh_id = 'WMD1'
and uc_reg_table_name = 'RCVTRK'
and uc_rule_grp_id = 'OSSI-RCVTRK-CREATED'
and uc_rule_subgrp_id = 'GLOBAL-MAP'
and uc_pk_col = 'trknum'
and uc_data_col = 'trknum'
and comflg = 1
